lines.text: What am I talking about? I just stuffed my dead biology teacher into the cupboard. Things are not allright.
I don't get mad, I bake.
We have a saying, girlfriends come, and girlfriends go, but best friends are forever.
While I'm here baking my face off, he's
probably out there having the time of his life.

[to Sarah]
Contrary to popular belief, there is a hell, and you're standing in it.
